            <description><![CDATA[<br>100 Days of SwiftUI<br>Day014 optionals, nil coalescing, and checkpoint 9<br>昨天晚上学完竟然忘记发了🥲过了一遍教程，完成教程后的题目。今天完成checkpoint9。<br><picture><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fto-NqHjup5OPyxjHUN5qmErpl3Sv2.jpg/strip/format/webp" type="image/webp"><source srcset="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fto-NqHjup5OPyxjHUN5qmErpl3Sv2.jpg" type="image/jpeg"><img referrerpolicy="no-referrer" src="https://cdn.jellow.site/Fto-NqHjup5OPyxjHUN5qmErpl3Sv2.jpg"></picture>]]></description>
